#X text 30 32 ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────;
#X text 30 50 Two novelty projectors run in parallel: ns_seq_features (rendered-sequence BC \, 24-d \,;
#X text 30 64 fully agnostic to MIDI/sample/param semantics) and ns_ast_features (AST-shape BC \, 40-d).;
#X text 30 78 Each feeds its own ns_archive instance. The OR-style admission gate ([max] of the two);
#X text 30 92 novelty scores) admits offspring that are novel in EITHER space — phenotypic OR genotypic.;
#X text 30 106 Quality (ns_quality) is the same hard gate as evo3 \, also fully domain-agnostic.;
